wikipedia_page.main: Oliver Edward "Olly" Westbury (born 2 July 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his List A debut for Worcestershire against the West Indies A in a tri-series warm-up match on 19 June 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for Worcestershire in the 2018 t20 Blast on 10 August 2018. He made his first-class debut for Worcestershire in the 2018 County Championship on 10 September 2018.
